<h2>âš  Stock Alert: Multiple Products</h2>

<p>Dear Admin,</p>

<p>The stock levels for the following products are too low to fulfill recent orders:</p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
	<thead>
		<tr>
			<th>Product Name</th>
			<th>ID</th>
			<th>Requested Quantity</th>
			<th>Available Stock</th>
		</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		{% for item in lowStockItems %}
			<tr>
				<td>{{ item.product.name }}</td>
				<td>{{ item.product.id }}</td>
				<td>{{ item.requested }}</td>
				<td>{{ item.available }}</td>
			</tr>
		{% endfor %}
	</tbody>
</table>

<p style="color: red;">
	<strong>Action Required:</strong>
	Please restock or disable these products to prevent overselling.</p>

<p>Thank you,<br>Your Store System</p>
